[{"id":"VR914717","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a diagram of an incident light moving downward through air and perpendicular to a surface of thin film on glass.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR914717.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Light is normally incident on a piece of glass that is coated with a thin layer of film, as shown in the figure. The film and the glass have indexes of refraction <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"n sub film, end sub, equals 1.20\"><math alttext=\"n sub film, end sub, equals 1.20\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>n</mi><mtext>film</mtext></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1.20</mn></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"n sub glass, end sub, equals 1.50\"><math alttext=\"n sub glass, end sub, equals 1.50\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>n</mi><mtext>glass</mtext></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1.50</mn></math></span></span>, respectively, and the light has a frequency of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"5.00 times 10 to the fourteenth power hertz\"><math alttext=\"5.00 times 10 to the fourteenth power hertz\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>5.00</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mn>14</mn></msup><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>Hz</mtext></math></span></span>. What is the minimum nonzero thickness of film that would result in the most intense reflection of light from the film and glass?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR914717_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"125 nanometers\"><math alttext=\"125 nanometers\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>125</mn><mtext>​</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>nm</mtext></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"150 nanometers\"><math alttext=\"150 nanometers\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>150</mn><mtext>​</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>nm</mtext></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"250 nanometers\"><math alttext=\"250 nanometers\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>250</mn><mtext>​</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>nm</mtext></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"300 nanometers\"><math alttext=\"300 nanometers\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>300</mn><mtext>​</mtext><mspace width=\"0.2em\"></mspace><mtext>nm</mtext></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]